.SS "icmp MODULE OPTIONS"
.TP
\-ct\ \fInum\fR
Set ICMP \fBmessage type\fR to \fInum\fR {0..255}.  Default: ICMP_ECHO (8)
for IPv4, or ICMP6_ECHO_REQUEST (128) for IPv6 packet.
.TP
\-cd\ \fInum\fR
Set ICMP \fBcode\fR to \fInum\fR {0..255}. Default:\ 0
.TP
\-cc\ \fInum\fR
Set ICMP \fBchecksum\fR to \fInum\fR {0.0xffff}.  Default:\ auto
